title: Storm Hawks Season 1 Complete [Dubbed English]
description:
Storm Hawks Season 1 Complete




The Storm Hawks head to Terra Atmosia to register as an official Sky Knight squadron, only to be rejected because of Aerrow's age. Shortly thereafter, the leader of the Red Eagles, Carver, tries to steal the Aurora Stone, the most powerful crystal in Atmos, from the beaconing tower in Atmosia. Although Aerrow is able to defeat him, things go from bad to worse when Master Cyclonis sends the Dark Ace to finish Carver's mission. Aerrow faces his first battle with the Dark Ace and loses his first battle. Dark Ace then allows Aerrow live so Aerrow could savour his defeat. The Storm Hawks are unable to fend off the fleet of Cyclonians. Aerrow and the Storm Hawks then decide to go to Cyclonia and get the Aurora Stone back from Cyclonis and her machine of evil
